        <p>Naval officer. Mate on HMS <hi rend="italic">Beagle</hi>, 1831–6. Lieutenant on HMS <hi rend="italic">Alligator</hi>, serving off the coast of Australia and the East Indies, 1837–41. His last period of sea duty was as commander in the Coast Guard, 1841–8. Captain, 1857. Government emigration officer in Glasgow, 1861.</p></note>
